<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>OAuth2 Mock Server</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14pt; margin: 40px; }
        .endpoint { background: #f5f5f5; padding: 15px; margin: 10px 0; border-radius: 5px; }
        code { background: #e0e0e0; padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; }
        .user-list { margin: 20px 0; }
        .user-item { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 5px; border-left: 4px solid #007bff; }
        .user-item h4 { margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #333; }
        .user-item p { margin: 5px 0; color: #666; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>OAuth2 Mock Server</h1>
    <div>This is a mock OAuth2 authorization server for testing purposes.</div>
    <div>After authorization you will be redirected to 
        <div class="endpoint">{{redirect_uri}} </div>  
    </div>
    
    <h3>These users are available for OAuth2 authorization:</h2>
    <div class="user-list">
        {{#each users}} 
        <div class="user-item">
                    <h3><a href="/authorize?login={{login}}&{{../auth_params}}">{{login}}</a></a></h4>
                    <p>{{description}}</p>
                </div>
        {{/each}}
    </div>

    <h2>Test Client:</h2>
    <p>You can use any client_id and client_secret for testing. The server accepts all valid OAuth2 flows.</p>


    <h2>Available Endpoints:</h2>
    
    <div class="endpoint">
        <h3>Authorization Endpoint</h3>
        <p><code>GET /authorize</code></p>
        <p>Parameters: response_type, client_id, redirect_uri, scope, state, code_challenge, code_challenge_method</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="endpoint">
        <h3>Token Endpoint</h3>
        <p><code>POST /token</code></p>
        <p>Parameters: grant_type, code, redirect_uri, client_id, client_secret, code_verifier, refresh_token</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="endpoint">
        <h3>User Info Endpoint</h3>
        <p><code>GET /userinfo</code></p>
        <p>Headers: Authorization: Bearer &lt;access_token&gt;</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="endpoint">
        <h3>OpenID Connect Configuration</h3>
        <p><code>GET /.well-known/openid_configuration</code></p>
    </div>
    
</body>
</html>
